### Create a new GUID [PUT]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            x-api-key: api_key_value
            x-token: token_value

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {
            "data": {
                "guid": "e0f1b2c8-d48f-4141-be90-cd05679083e6",
                "status": "issued"
            }
        }

### Assign a GUID to entity [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            x-api-key: api_key_value
            x-token: token_value

    + Body

            {
                "guid": "21350d73-5d4c-42f5-b837-e6cf0d116255",
                "assign_to": "EMMA"
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "data": {
                "guid": "e0f1b2c8-d48f-4141-be90-cd05679083e6",
                "status": "assigned",
                "assigned_to": "EMMA"
            }
        }